OL,3,CEmpty vodka bottles found inside drunk
OL,4,Clorry driver's HGV
OL,6,FA drunk lorry driver who drove into a
OL,7,Fholiday park in Sussex had empty vodka
OL,8,Fbottles inside his HGV.
OL,10,FJanis Rimovics, 50, was driving a 44-
OL,11,Ftonne articulated lorry, whilst more
OL,12,Fthan three times the legal alcohol
OL,13,Flimit, when he struck a parked vehicle
OL,14,Fin Church Lane, Pagham.
OL,16,FHe then drove into a nearby holiday
OL,17,Fpark which was busy with families and
OL,18,Fchildren on August 25.
