OL,6,FRimovics tried to reverse his vehicle
OL,7,Fout of a dead end but was unable to
OL,8,Fcomplete the manoeuvre, and then fell
OL,9,Fasleep in his cab.
OL,11,FPolice were called to the scene and
OL,12,Fwhen officers arrived, they found
OL,13,FRimovics too intoxicated to stand.
OL,15,FThey also found empty vodka bottles
OL,16,Finside the cab of his HGV.
OL,18,FRimovics provided a breath alcohol
OL,19,Freading of 128 microgrammes (g) of
OL,20,Falcohol per 100 millilitres (ml) of
OL,21,Fbreath.
