OL,6,FThe legal limit is 35g of alcohol per
OL,7,F100ml of breath.
OL,9,FSpeaking after the case, Acting
OL,10,FSergeant Steven Lambeth from the Roads
OL,11,FPolicing Unit, said: "Rimovics was in
OL,12,Fcharge of a large lorry while more
OL,13,Fthan three times the legal alcohol
OL,14,Flimit.
OL,16,F"He was in no fit state to drive and
OL,17,Fwas barely able to stand, let alone
OL,18,Fdrive a vehicle, when he arrived in
OL,19,Fcustody.
