OL,6,F"Drink-driving is one of the main
OL,7,Freasons why people are killed or
OL,8,Fseriously injured on our roads.
OL,10,F"Rimovics posed a serious risk not
OL,11,Fonly to himself, but to every other
OL,12,Froad user, he is lucky not to have
OL,13,Fcaused serious harm that night.
OL,15,F"We are pleased that a dangerous
OL,16,Fdriver has been taken off our roads."
OL,18,FRimovics, of Station Estate Road,
OL,19,FFeltham, was sentenced to four months
OL,20,Fin prison. He was disqualified from
OL,21,Fdriving for 18 months.
